  "description": "A collection of 72 framework-agnostic Web Components (ce-* UI building blocks + lesson-* educational widgets) built on Lit, including chat-surface and feedback-UI primitives for LLM applications. Each component is self-describing via a validated *.meta.json. Ship as a single bundle, auto-register everything, or tree-shake down to the tags you use.",
